{"title":"AngularJS中的配置块(config)","slug":"AngularJS中的配置快(config)","date":"2017-09-21T11:59:32.841Z","updated":"2017-09-21T12:42:54.166Z","comments":true,"excerpt":"","content":"<blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"1-配置块\"><a href=\"#1-配置块\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1. 配置块.\"></a>1. 配置块.</h2><ul>\n<li>在配置运行阶段,ng允许我们对ng内置的一些服务做一些修改.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"2-如何进行针对服务进行配置\"><a href=\"#2-如何进行针对服务进行配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.如何进行针对服务进行配置.\"></a>2.如何进行针对服务进行配置.</h2><ul>\n<li>模块对象(app)提供了一个方法: config<ul>\n<li>功能: 就是对内置的服务进行修改 对内置的服务进行配置.</li>\n<li>参数: 是1个数组,数组前面写上你要配置的服务对应的Provider  <figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">$log   $logProvider</div><div class=\"line\">$http  $httpProvider</div><div class=\"line\"></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//每一个服务都有一个对应的Provider</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n<pre><code>- 最后一个元素是一个回调函数，通过形参将这个Provider注入\n</code></pre><blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"实现：\"><a href=\"#实现：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"实现：\"></a>实现：</h2><figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">body</span> <span class=\"attr\">ng-app</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"hmApp\"</span>&gt;</span></div><div class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">div</span> <span class=\"attr\">ng-contorller</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"hmCtrl\"</span>&gt;</span></div><div class=\"line\">        <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">h2</span>&gt;</span>&#123;&#123;name|firstBig&#125;&#125;<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">h2</span>&gt;</span></div><div class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">div</span>&gt;</span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">body</span>&gt;</span></div><div class=\"line\"></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">script</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"undefined\"></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"javascript\">    <span class=\"keyword\">var</span> app = angular.module(<span class=\"string\">\"hmApp\"</span>,[]);</span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"javascript\">    app.config([<span class=\"string\">\"$logProvider\"</span>,<span class=\"string\">\"$filterProvider\"</span>,<span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span>(<span class=\"params\">$logProvider,$filterProvider</span>)</span>&#123;</span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"javascript\">        $logProvider.debugEnabled(<span class=\"literal\">false</span>);</span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"javascript\">        $filterProvider.register(<span class=\"string\">\"firstBig\"</span>,<span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span>(<span class=\"params\"></span>)</span>&#123;</span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"javascript\">            retrun <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span>(<span class=\"params\">data</span>)</span>&#123;</span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"javascript\">                <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> data[<span class=\"number\">0</span>].toUpperCase() + data.slice(<span class=\"number\">1</span>);</span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"undefined\">            &#125;</span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"undefined\">        &#125;)</span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"undefined\">    &#125;]);</span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"javascript\">    app.controller(<span class=\"string\">\"hmCtrl\"</span>,[<span class=\"string\">\"$scope\"</span>,<span class=\"string\">\"$log\"</span>,<span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span>(<span class=\"params\">$scope,$log</span>)</span>&#123;</span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"javascript\">        $log.debug(<span class=\"string\">\"这是debug信息\"</span>);</span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"javascript\">        $log.error(<span class=\"string\">\"error!\"</span>);</span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"javascript\">        $scope.name = <span class=\"string\">\"hahah\"</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"undefined\">    &#125;])</span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"undefined\"></span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">script</span>&gt;</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></blockquote>\n","categories":[{"name":"Angular","path":"api/categories/Angular.json"}],"tags":[]}